&lt;/div&gt;\r\n            \r\n            &lt;div class=\"overview-grid\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"overview-main\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"overview-lead\"&gt;\r\n                        FlowLayer is a conceptual navigation application that introduces &lt;strong&gt;emotional routing&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî \r\n                        a paradigm shift from optimizing purely for time or distance to optimizing for the \r\n                        &lt;em&gt;quality of the journey itself&lt;/em&gt;.\r\n                    &lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"overview-text\"&gt;\r\n                        In an era where autonomous vehicles and smart infrastructure are becoming reality, \r\n                        we asked: what if navigation understood not just where you want to go, but how you \r\n                        want to feel when you get there?\r\n                    &lt;/p&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n    &lt;/section&gt;\r\n\r\n    &lt;!-- Problem Section --&gt;\r\n    &lt;section class=\"section problem\" id=\"problem\"&gt;\r\n        &lt;div class=\"section-container\"&gt;\r\n            &lt;div class=\"section-header\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;span class=\"section-number\"&gt;02&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                &lt;h2 class=\"section-title\"&gt;The Problem&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            \r\n            &lt;div class=\"problem-content\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"problem-statement\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"quote-mark\"&gt;\"&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;blockquote&gt;\r\n                        Navigation apps optimize for efficiency, but ignore the human experience. \r\n                        The fastest route isn't always the best route.\r\n                    &lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                \r\n                &lt;div class=\"pain-points\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"pain-point\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"pain-icon\"&gt;üò§&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;One-Size-Fits-All&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p&gt;Current apps treat all drivers the same, ignoring personal preferences, moods, and context.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"pain-point\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"pain-icon\"&gt;üò∞&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Stress Amplification&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p&gt;Fastest routes often involve highway merges, heavy traffic, and aggressive driving conditions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"pain-point\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"pain-icon\"&gt;üèÉ&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Journey Ignored&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p&gt;Beautiful scenic roads, interesting neighborhoods, and memorable experiences are bypassed entirely.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"pain-point\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"pain-icon\"&gt;ü§ñ&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;No Emotional Intelligence&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p&gt;Navigation doesn't adapt to whether you're rushing to work or enjoying a Sunday drive.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n                &lt;div class=\"research-insights\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;h3&gt;Research Insights&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"insight-cards\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"insight-card\"&gt;\r\n                            &lt;div class=\"insight-stat\"&gt;67%&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                            &lt;p&gt;of drivers report navigation-related stress at least once a week&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"insight-card\"&gt;\r\n                            &lt;div class=\"insight-stat\"&gt;43%&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                            &lt;p&gt;would take a longer route if it meant a more pleasant drive&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"insight-card\"&gt;\r\n                            &lt;div class=\"insight-stat\"&gt;89%&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                            &lt;p&gt;want navigation that understands their preferences better&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n    &lt;/section&gt;\r\n\r\n    &lt;!-- Solution Section --&gt;\r\n    &lt;section class=\"section solution\" id=\"solution\"&gt;\r\n        &lt;div class=\"section-container\"&gt;\r\n            &lt;div class=\"section-header\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;span class=\"section-number\"&gt;03&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                &lt;h2 class=\"section-title\"&gt;The Solution&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            \r\n            &lt;div class=\"solution-intro\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;h3&gt;Introducing Vibe-Based Routing&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n                &lt;p&gt;\r\n                    FlowLayer introduces four distinct \"vibes\" that transform how routes are calculated, \r\n                    each optimizing for a different aspect of the driving experience.\r\n                &lt;/p&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n            &lt;div class=\"vibes-showcase\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"vibe-card-large\" style=\"--vibe-color: #ff9f1c\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-header-card\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"vibe-emoji\"&gt;‚ö°&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Fastest&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-description\"&gt;Direct ‚Ä¢ Quick ‚Ä¢ Highway&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-detail\"&gt;Takes major highways with minimal stops to reach your destination as fast as possible.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-example\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-label\"&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-route\"&gt;Highway 101 Express ‚Äî 12 min&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n                &lt;div class=\"vibe-card-large\" style=\"--vibe-color: #00f5d4\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-header-card\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"vibe-emoji\"&gt;üåä&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Easy &amp; Chill&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-description\"&gt;Calm ‚Ä¢ Simple ‚Ä¢ Low-Stress&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-detail\"&gt;Avoids highways and heavy traffic. Sticks to smooth roads and easy turns for a relaxed drive.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-example\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-label\"&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-route\"&gt;Riverside Drive ‚Äî 22 min&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n                &lt;div class=\"vibe-card-large\" style=\"--vibe-color: #06d6a0\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-header-card\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"vibe-emoji\"&gt;üèûÔ∏è&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Scenic&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-description\"&gt;Views ‚Ä¢ Nature ‚Ä¢ Relax&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-detail\"&gt;Follows coastal roads, lakesides, forests, and lookout points for beautiful scenery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-example\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-label\"&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-route\"&gt;Lakefront Parkway ‚Äî 35 min&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n                &lt;div class=\"vibe-card-large\" style=\"--vibe-color: #f72585\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-header-card\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"vibe-emoji\"&gt;üé¢&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Adventure&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-description\"&gt;Twists ‚Ä¢ Fun ‚Ä¢ Detours&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p class=\"vibe-detail\"&gt;Uses mountain roads, winding curves, unique landmarks, clubs, and exciting detours.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"vibe-example\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-label\"&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                        &lt;span class=\"example-route\"&gt;Downtown Loop ‚Äî 28 min&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n            &lt;div class=\"solution-features\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"feature-block\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"feature-visual\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"feature-icon-large\"&gt;üéØ&lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"feature-text\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Contextual Intelligence&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p&gt;Routes adapt based on time of day, weather conditions, traffic &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"feature-text\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;h4&gt;Real-Time Pulse&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p&gt;Live metrics show current city conditions ‚Äî traffic levels, active events, weather status ‚Äî helping you make informed decisions about your journey.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=\"feature-block\"&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=\"feature-visual\"&gt;\r\n                        &lt;div Preview&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p&gt;AI-powered predictions show what to expect on each route ‚Äî highlights, stress levels, points of interest ‚Äî before you start driving.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n    &lt;/section&gt;\r\n\r\n    &lt;!-- Features Section &lt;span&gt;üó∫Ô∏è&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;h4&gt;Emotional Map Visualization&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p&gt;Color-coded overlays show &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    &lt;h4&gt;Turn-by-Turn Navigation&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p&gt;Beautiful navigation interface with real-time emotional monitoring and smooth road content.innerHTML = &#96;\n        &lt;div class=\"prediction-vibe\"&gt;${pred.emoji}&lt;/div&gt;\n        &lt;div class=\"prediction-label\"&gt;${pred.label}&lt;/div&gt;\n        &lt;div   &lt;/div&gt;\n            &lt;span class=\"confidence-text\"&gt;${pred.confidence}% match&lt;/span&gt;\n        &lt;/div&gt;\n    &#96;;\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// CANVAS RENDERING\n// ============================================\n\nfunction hexToRgba(hex, alpha) {\n    const r = parseInt(hex.slice(1, 3), 16);\n    const g = parseInt(hex.slice(3, 5), 16);\n    const b = parseInt(hex.slice(5, 7), 16);\n    return &#96;rgba(${r}, ${g}, ${b}, ${alpha})&#96;;\n}\n\n// City Map\nfunction initCityMap() {\n    const canvas = document.getElementById('cityMap');\n    if (!canvas) return;\n    \n    const container = canvas.parentElement;\n    const rect = container.getBoundingClientRect();\n    \n    canvas.width = rect.width * 2;\n    canvas.height = rect.height * 2;\n    canvas.style.width = rect.width + 'px';\n    canvas.style.height = rect.height + 'px';\n    \n    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n    ctx.scale(2, 2);\n    \n    drawCityMap(ctx, rect.width, rect.height);\n}\n\nfunction drawCityMap(ctx, width, height) {\n    // Background\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#0a0a10';\n    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, width, height);\n    \n    // Grid\n    ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)';\n    ctx.lineWidth = 1;\n    for (let x = 0; x &lt; width; x += 25) {\n        ctx.beginPath();\n        ctx.moveTo(x, 0);\n        ctx.lineTo(x, height);\n        ctx.stroke();\n    }\n    for (let y = 0; y &lt; height; y += 25) {\n        ctx.beginPath();\n        ctx.moveTo(0, y);\n        ctx.lineTo(width, y);\n        ctx.stroke();\n    }\n    \n    // Streets\n    ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08)';\n    ctx.lineWidth = 3;\n    [0.25, 0.5, 0.75].forEach(r =&gt; {\n        ctx.beginPath();\n        ctx.moveTo(0, height * r);\n        ctx.lineTo(width, height * r);\n        ctx.stroke();\n    });\n    [0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8].forEach(r =&gt; {\n        ctx.beginPath();\n        ctx.moveTo(width * r, 0);\n        ctx.lineTo(width * r, height);\n        ctx.stroke();\n    });\n    \n    const vibe = vibes[state.selectedVibe];\n    const pois = pointsOfInterest[state.selectedVibe] || [];\n    \n    // Draw POIs for current vibe\n    pois.forEach(poi =&gt; {\n        drawPOI(ctx, width * poi.x, height * poi.y, vibe.color, poi.icon, poi.name);\n    });\n    \n    // Draw route based on vibe\n    const routeColor = vibe.color;\n    let routePoints;\n    \n    if (state.selectedVibe === 'fastest') {\n        // Straight highway route\n        routePoints = [\n            { x: width * 0.1, y: height * 0.85 },\n            { x: width * 0.3, y: height * 0.6 },\n            { x: width * 0.5, y: height * 0.4 },\n            { x: width * 0.7, y: height * 0.25 },\n            { x: width * 0.9, y: height * 0.15 }\n        ];\n    } else if (state.selectedVibe === 'scenic') {\n        // Curvy scenic route passing lakes and viewpoints\n        routePoints = [\n            { x: width * 0.1, y: height * 0.85 },\n            { x: width * 0.2, y: height * 0.4 }, // Near lake\n            { x: width * 0.4, y: height * 0.55 },\n            { x: width * 0.55, y: height * 0.65 }, // Through forest\n            { x: width * 0.75, y: height * 0.3 }, // Near bridge view\n            { x: width * 0.9, y: height * 0.15 }\n        ];\n    } else if (state.selectedVibe === 'adventure') {\n        // Winding route through exciting areas\n        routePoints = [\n            { x: width * 0.1, y: height * 0.85 },\n            { x: width * 0.25, y: height * 0.6 },\n            { x: width * 0.35, y: height * 0.55 }, // Neon district\n            { x: width * 0.5, y: height * 0.45 },\n            { x: width * 0.65, y: height * 0.5 }, // Music row\n            { x: width * 0.75, y: height * 0.35 },\n            { x: width * 0.9, y: height * 0.15 }\n        ];\n    } else {\n        // Chill - smooth easy route\n        routePoints = [\n            { x: width * 0.1, y: height * 0.85 },\n            { x: width * 0.25, y: height * 0.7 },\n            { x: width * 0.4, y: height * 0.55 },\n            { x: width * 0.6, y: height * 0.4 },\n            { x: width * 0.75, y: height * 0.3 },\n            { x: width * 0.9, y: height * 0.15 }\n        ];\n    }\n    \n    drawRoute(ctx, routePoints, routeColor);\n    \n    // Markers\n    drawMarker(ctx, routePoints[0].x, routePoints[0].y, routeColor, true);\n    drawMarker(ctx, routePoints[routePoints.length-1].x, routePoints[routePoints.length-1].y, '#9b5de5', false);\n}\n\nfunction drawPOI(ctx, x, y, color, icon, name) {\n    // Glow\n    ctx.fillStyle = hexToRgba(color, 0.2);\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(x, y, 35, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n    ctx.fill();\n    \n    ctx.fillStyle = hexToRgba(color, 0.4);\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(x, y, 20, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n    ctx.fill();\n    \n    // Icon background\n    ctx.fillStyle = hexToRgba(color, 0.8);\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(x, y, 12, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n    ctx.fill();\n    \n    // Icon\n    ctx.font = '14px Arial';\n    ctx.textAlign = 'center';\n    ctx.textBaseline = 'middle';\n    ctx.fillText(icon, x, y);\n    \n    // Label\n    ctx.font = '10px Outfit';\n    ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,0.7)';\n    ctx.fillText(name, x, y + 25);\n}\n\nfunction drawRoute(ctx, points, color) {\n    if (points.length &lt; 2) return;\n    \n    ctx.strokeStyle = color;\n    ctx.lineWidth = 4;\n    ctx.lineCap = 'round';\n    ctx.lineJoin = 'round';\n    \n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.moveTo(points[0].x, points[0].y);\n    \n    for (let i = 1; i &lt; points.length - 1; i++) {\n        const xc = (points[i].x + points[i + 1].x) / 2;\n        const yc = (points[i].y + points[i + 1].y) / 2;\n        ctx.quadraticCurveTo(points[i].x, points[i].y, xc, yc);\n    }\n    ctx.lineTo(points[points.length-1].x, points[points.length-1].y);\n    \n    ctx.shadowColor = color;\n    ctx.shadowBlur = 15;\n    ctx.stroke();\n    ctx.shadowBlur = 0;\n}\n\nfunction drawMarker(ctx, x, y, color, isStart) {\n    ctx.fillStyle = hexToRgba(color, 0.3);\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(x, y, 14, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n    ctx.fill();\n    \n    ctx.fillStyle = color;\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(x, y, 8, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n    ctx.fill();\n    \n    ctx.fillStyle = '#0a0a10';\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(x, y, 4, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n    ctx.fill();\n}\n\n// Phone Map\nfunction initPhoneMap() {\n    const canvas = document.getElementById('phoneMapCanvas');\n    if (!canvas) return;\n    \n    const container = canvas.parentElement;\n    canvas.width = container.offsetWidth * 2;\n    canvas.height = container.offsetHeight * 2;\n    canvas.style.width = container.offsetWidth + 'px';\n    canvas.style.height = container.offsetHeight + 'px';\n    \n    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n    ctx.scale(2, 2);\n    \n    drawPhoneMap(ctx, container.offsetWidth, container.offsetHeight);\n}\n\nfunction drawPhoneMap(ctx, width, height) {\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#050508';\n    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, width, height);\n    \n    // Grid\n    ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)';\n    ctx.lineWidth = 1;\n    for (let x = 0; x &lt; width; x += 20) {\n        ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(x, 0); ctx.lineTo(x, height); ctx.stroke();\n    }\n    for (let y = 0; y &lt; height; y += 20) {\n        ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(0, y); ctx.lineTo(width, y); ctx.stroke();\n    }\n    \n    const vibe = vibes[state.selectedVibe];\n    const pois = pointsOfInterest[state.selectedVibe] || [];\n    \n    // Draw some POIs\n    pois.slice(0, 3).forEach((poi, i) =&gt; {\n        const px = 50 + (i * 80);\n        const py = height * 0.35 + (i % 2 === 0 ? 0 : 50);\n        drawPOI(ctx, px, py, vibe.color, poi.icon, '');\n    });\n    \n    // Route\n    const color = vibe.color;\n    const routePoints = [\n        { x: 35, y: height * 0.72 },\n        { x: 80, y: height * 0.55 },\n        { x: 140, y: height * 0.4 },\n        { x: 200, y: height * 0.3 },\n        { x: width - 55, y: height * 0.18 }\n    ];\n    \n    drawRoute(ctx, routePoints, color);\n    drawMarker(ctx, routePoints[0].x, routePoints[0].y, color, true);\n    drawMarker(ctx, routePoints[routePoints.length-1].x, routePoints[routePoints.length-1].y, '#9b5de5', false);\n}\n\n// Nav Map\nfunction initNavMap() {\n    const canvas = document.getElementById('navMapCanvas');\n    if (!canvas) return;\n    \n    const container = canvas.parentElement;\n    canvas.width = container.offsetWidth * 2;\n    canvas.height = container.offsetHeight * 2;\n    canvas.style.width = container.offsetWidth + 'px';\n    canvas.style.height = container.offsetHeight + 'px';\n    \n    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n    ctx.scale(2, 2);\n    \n    const width = container.offsetWidth;\n    const height = container.offsetHeight;\n    const vibe = vibes[state.selectedVibe];\n    \n    ctx.fillStyle = '#050508';\n    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, width, height);\n    \n    // Grid\n    ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)';\n    for (let x = 0; x &lt; width; x += 25) {\n        ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(x, 0); ctx.lineTo(x, height); ctx.stroke();\n    }\n    for (let y = 0; y &lt; height; y += 25) {\n        ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(0, y); ctx.lineTo(width, y); ## Changes Made

### 1. **Removed Desktop Dashboard** 
- The entire right-side dashboard with metrics, vibe selector, route comparison, and future highway planner has been removed
- The app is now mobile-only, full-screen

### 2. **Removed Status Bar**
- Time display (`9:41`) and battery indicator (`‚ö° 87%`) removed from the phone simulation

### 3. **Made iPhone-Responsive**
- Added proper viewport meta tags for iOS
- Added safe area inset support for notched iPhones (X, 11, 12, 13, 14, 15 series)
- Added specific breakpoints for iPhone SE, 6/7/8, Plus models, and Pro Max
- Added landscape mode support

### 4. **Added Destination Selection Screen**
- New screen with search bar for destinations
- 6 fake recent destinations (Golden Gate Bridge, Fisherman's Wharf, Twin Peaks, Chinatown, Palace of Fine Arts, Alcatraz Ferry)
- 2 saved places (Home, Work)
- Back button navigation

### 5. **Made Bottom Navigation Sticky**
- Bottom nav is now always visible at the bottom of the screen
- Properly handles safe area insets for iPhones with home indicator

### 6. **Flow Update**
- New Route ‚Üí Destination Screen ‚Üí Vibe Selection ‚Üí Map ‚Üí Navigation
